How it works

Ever wondered how to reduce CO2 emissions from your car ride or flight? Investment in renewables can solve this problem and bring you money!
My Power Farm receives and processes applications from developers or owners of green power plants
Independent expert panel verifies project data and reports
You come up with informed investment decision offsetting your CO2 emissions
You offset your CO2 footprint and track the performance in the personal cabinet receiving returns
